<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm">
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Axis_placement_3d">
An <b>Axis_placement_3d</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Axis_placement"/> that is three dimensional.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_intersection">
<note> The text description for this Application Object has not been fully updated to agree with the EXPRESS.</note>

A <b>Shape_definition_3d_intersection</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Foundation_representation:arm:Foundation_representation_arm.Representation_relationship"/>. A Volume_shape_intersection may be one of <express_ref linkend="Layered_inconnect_module_3d_shape:arm:Layered_inconnect_module_3d_shape_arm.Edge_segment_cross_section"/>, or
 <express_ref linkend="Pre_defined_datum_symbol:arm:Pre_defined_datum_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_perpendicular_datum_plane_symbol_3d_2d_relationship"/>, or
 <express_ref linkend="Pre_defined_datum_symbol:arm:Pre_defined_datum_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_perpendicular_datum_axis_symbol_3d_2d_relationship"/>, or
 <express_ref linkend="Pre_defined_datum_symbol:arm:Pre_defined_datum_symbol_arm.Pre_defined_parallel_datum_axis_symbol_3d_2d_relationship"/>. A <b>Shape_definition_3d_intersection</b> is the projection into two dimensions 
of a three-dimensional shape based on the intersection of a plane with the three-dimensional shape.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_intersection.projected_volume">
the <b>projected_volume</b> specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Unknown:arm:Unknown_arm.Three_dimensional_shape"/> for the <b>Shape_definition_3d_intersection</b>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_intersection.surface_intersection_result"></ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_intersection.planar_shape_origin">
the <b>planar_shape_origin</b> specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Layered_2d_shape:arm:Layered_2d_shape_arm.Axis_placement_2d"/> for the <b>Shape_definition_3d_intersection</b>.  The Axis_placement_2d shall define the two dimensional coordinate system.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_intersection.orientation_intersection_plane">
the <b>orientation_intersection_plane</b> specifies the role of the <express_ref linkend="Layered_3d_shape:arm:Layered_3d_shape_arm.Axis_placement_3d"/> for the <b>Shape_definition_3d_intersection</b>.  The Z axis of the Axis_placement_3d shall define the normal of the plane.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Layered_3d_shape_arm.Shape_definition_3d_plane_projection">
<note> The text description for this Application Object has not been fully updated to agree with the EXPRESS.</note>

A <b>Shape_definition_3d_plane_projection</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Foundation_representation:arm:Foundation_representation_arm.Representation_relationship"/>.
</ext_description>
